cab.content: 5W20RAILWAYMSN'SSTRIKE.BOARD OF TRADE .Bulletin No.8*Friday 27th Sept.1916.10.. a. m.It is reported from the Railway Executive Committeethat matters are easier everywhere this morning, except on the London & South Western and the Brighton Railway where there is not much alteration. The situation at Liverpool is also much the same as last night, but an appreciable improvement at Stratford on the Great Eastern Railway is expected. i
